bilingual.source: But he was nowhere to be seen.
Some are ill or have nowhere to stay.
bilingual.target: 有些生病了或者无处可去。

bilingual.source: The street turned into a river and we were going nowhere.
bilingual.target: 街道变成了河流，我们无处可去。

bilingual.source: The missing cat was nowhere in the house.
bilingual.target: 那只失踪的猫在房子里无处可见。

bilingual.source: He felt like he was going nowhere in his career.
bilingual.target: 他觉得自己的事业无处可去。

bilingual.source: The nakedness of the truth left him nowhere to hide.
bilingual.target: 赤裸的真相让他无处可藏。

bilingual.source: He looked like a stray cur, with nowhere to go.
bilingual.target: 他看起来像一个丧家之犬，无处可去。

bilingual.source: The road led nowhere, so we had to turn back.
bilingual.target: 这条路无处可通，所以我们不得不掉头。

bilingual.source: I looked for my keys, but they were nowhere to be found.
bilingual.target: 我找了我的钥匙，但它们无处可寻。

bilingual.source: She searched for her lost ring, but it was nowhere to be found.
bilingual.target: 她找了她丢失的戒指，但它无处可寻。

list.abstract: no where是一个全新的创意时尚电子商务品牌，本着“快乐自由，无处不在”的品牌精神，和着潮流的节拍，为年轻女性们打造最专业、最时尚、最潮流的服饰产品。
nowhere是一个英语单词，可以用作形容词、副词和名词，可以翻译为无处、任何地方，等等。

yingyinNormal.en: Already cut twice this season, Sleeping on a teammate's couch, because he had nowhere else to go, And, suddenly, Jeremy Lin is the toast of Manhattan.
yingyinNormal.zh: 本赛季两次被裁，因为无处可去而只能睡在队友的沙发上，而一夜之间，他成了曼哈顿的宠儿

yingyinNormal.en: There's nowhere that's safe. Remember.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有安全的地方。记起来。

yingyinNormal.en: Nowhere, with no one doing nothing with nobody.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不在任何地方，没和任何人在一起，没和任何人做任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, that's odd. There's nowhere he could have got off?
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，很奇怪，没地方让他下车?

yingyinNormal.en: I was just frustrated because my career is going nowhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当时我因为事业不顺，内心严重受挫。

yingyinNormal.en: It's nowhere special, but it's on the way to everywhere special.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没什么特别的地方，不过...它的一切都将变得特别。

yingyinNormal.en: It came out of nowhere. The winds were blowing at 175 miles an hour.
yingyinNormal.zh: 飓风突然就来了。风速达到每小时175英里。

yingyinNormal.en: But not as vast as mine. And nowhere near as charming. Certainly no girls from Kungurat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但没有我的多。姿色也远远不及，他的后宫中肯定没有突厥女子。

yingyinNormal.en: A TV as if it appears from nowhere. That's the dream. Man, how did you afford this stuff?
yingyinNormal.zh: 凭空冒出来的电视，这是我的梦想，你哪来这么多钱？

yingyinNormal.en: Why are you with us? 'Cause as crazy as you two are, you're nowhere near as messed up as them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你为什么要跟着我们？因为不管你们俩再怎么不正常也比不上他们那样的混乱。

yingyinNormal.en: And I didn't see you nowhere when things started getting bad. So don't go give me no lectures.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事态变差的时候我也没看到你出现啊，所以别教我该怎么做。

yingyinNormal.en: So even though beauty may be skin deep, beauty is nowhere near as important as the army inside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以即使美丽就是肤浅的，但美丽却远没有内在的自己那么重要。

yingyinNormal.en: There's nowhere he could go. It's a straight run on the District Line between the two stations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他没地方可去，区域线两站之间是直线。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, it was the weirdest thing. They fire me and then out of nowhere, they just hire me back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是多么古怪呀。他们先是解雇我，然后又无缘无故重新聘用我。

yingyinNormal.en: You want to spread your wings, that's great. But you can't spread your wings and fly to nowhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想展翅高飞，这很好。但是你不能漫无目的得展翅高飞。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: Nowhere that you would understand, Dolores. Perhaps that's why I enjoy our conversations so much.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在一个你无法理解的地方，徳洛丽丝，或许正因如此，我才喜欢跟你交谈。

yingyinNormal.en: They told me this guy came from the outside who was a pro. He was fast. He fucking came out of nowhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们告诉我杀手从外面进来，是个职业杀手，动作麻利，不知道从哪里冒出来。

yingyinNormal.en: So, anyway, the other day, these pigs showed up out of nowhere, and it caused me a great deal of suspicion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，说正事，有一天这群猪不知从哪冒了出来，整件事让我觉得非常可疑。

yingyinNormal.en: There's no such thing as absolute power for us, except on the receiving end. Using fear will get you nowhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人类无权拥有绝对的权力，只能接受上帝的统治，用恐惧统治不会有好下场。

yingyinNormal.en: And then we had a little wine, we got to talking, and the next thing you know out of nowhere Ross comes on to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们边喝酒边聊天，接下来罗斯采取主动。

examination_example.sentence: People who do so probably live so cautiously that they go <highlight>nowhere</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这样做的人可能会非常谨慎，以至于他们的生活止步不前。
